        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'HNB1', 3: 'I\\'m keeping you safe through the night.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'HNB1', 3: 'Oh, and just call me HNB1—just like how HBG3 calls me.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Little Girl', 3: 'That\\'s not a name. It\\'s just a number. Don\\'t you two have any other names you call each other?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'HNB1', 3: 'You mean B1 or G3? That\\'s a name we call different Tai\\'E series with. Sometimes our bosses call us by nicknames to tell us apart. But that new hunk of steel doesn\\'t like calling me that.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Little Girl', 3: 'Are you friends?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'HNB1', 3: 'Well, that\\'s a pretty tough question. I don\\'t know if we count as friends. We\\'re just partners—not sure if he likes me that much though, but I guess it\\'s weird for a robot to have likes and dislikes. We just obey orders.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Little Girl', 3: 'But I think he actually cares about you...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'HNB1', 3: 'Really? Did he send you over here? I thought there\\'s just nothing but data in that brain of his...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'HNB1', 3: 'And why are you suddenly acting like a life coach? Aren\\'t you only eight or nine years old?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '4'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Little Girl', 3: 'I\\'m older than that! He\\'s just cleaning the room inside. I was just a little... a little worried about you.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
